lazyTrees

Class LazySearchTree.LazySTNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • lazyTrees.LazySearchTree.LazySTNode
  • Enclosing class:
    LazySearchTree<E extends java.lang.Comparable<? super E>>

    private class LazySearchTree.LazySTNode
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents each node of the binary search tree which implements lazy deletion. Each node has the data, a pointer to a left child, a pointer to the right child and a boolean attribute denoting whether the node has been marked as deleted.

    anuva
